OL,3,CMan found guilty of murder and cruelty
OL,4,Cof partner's toddler son
OL,6,FReporter Amy Sutton was at Teesside
OL,7,FCrown Court for the verdict
OL,9,FA man has been found guilty of the
OL,10,Fmurder and cruelty of his partner's
OL,11,Ftoddler who was left in his care.
OL,13,FCharlie Roberts was aged one year and
OL,14,F10 months when he suffered an
OL,15,Funsurvivable head injury, which
OL,16,Fprosecutors claimed during a trial was
OL,17,Fcaused by Christopher Stockton shaking
OL,18,For throwing him.
