OL,3,CMan found guilty of murder and cruelty
OL,4,Cof partner's toddler son
OL,6,FThe 38-year-old had stayed up late
OL,7,Fplaying video games the night before
OL,8,Ftoddler Charlie was left in his care
OL,9,Fon 12 January while his mother went
OL,10,Fout to an eye appointment.
OL,12,FStockton, of Neasham Road, denied
OL,13,Fmurder but was convicted at trial by a
OL,14,Fjury at Teesside Crown Court on
OL,15,FTuesday (10 December).
OL,17,FHe was also found guilty of a charge
OL,18,Fof child cruelty, for injuries caused
OL,19,Fto Charlie in the months before his
OL,20,Fdeath.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/15
