OL,3,CMan found guilty of murder and cruelty
OL,4,Cof partner's toddler son
OL,6,FCharlie's mother and Stockton's then
OL,7,Fpartner, Paula Roberts, 41, of Close
OL,8,FStreet, Darlington, previously pleaded
OL,9,Fguilty to child neglect after failing
OL,10,Fto act over a number of painful
OL,11,Finjuries suffered by her son.
OL,13,FStockton, who had moved in with
OL,14,FRoberts and her little boy just seven
OL,15,Fdays earlier, was in sole charge of
OL,16,FCharlie when he inflicted a severe
OL,17,Fhead injury which caused widespread
OL,18,Fbleeding on the brain.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/15
