OL,3,CMan found guilty of murder and cruelty
OL,4,Cof partner's toddler son
OL,6,FNicholas Lumley KC, prosecuting, told
OL,7,Fjurors: "The prosecution say that
OL,8,FChristopher Stockton ` and nobody else
OL,9,F` is responsible for Charlie's death;
OL,10,Fthat he shook or threw him with such
OL,11,Fviolence, deliberately and forcefully
OL,12,Fharming little Charlie."
OL,14,FThe mother had left the home minutes
OL,15,Fbefore to go for an eye test and
OL,16,FStockton, who was off work ill and who
OL,17,Fhad stayed up into the early hours
OL,18,Fplaying Xbox games, must have snapped
OL,19,Fthat January morning at the family
OL,20,Fhome in Darlington.
