OL,3,CMan found guilty of murder and cruelty
OL,4,Cof partner's toddler son
OL,6,FStockton rang 999 and could be heard
OL,7,Fon a recording repeatedly saying "come
OL,8,Fon mate" and "wakey wakey" to the
OL,9,Flittle boy, who was not breathing.
OL,11,FThe call-handler talked him through
OL,12,Fhow to perform CPR and at one point
OL,13,FStockton said he would pass out if he
OL,14,Ftried to count the compressions he was
OL,15,Fdoing on the toddler.
OL,17,FStockton was to tell paramedics,
OL,18,Fdoctors and the police that Charlie
OL,19,Fhad choked on a biscuit and that he
OL,20,Fpatted the child on the back and stuck
OL,21,Fhis fingers down the toddler's throat.
