OL,6,FStockton said Charlie became "floppy"
OL,7,Fand so he called 999.
OL,9,FThe toddler died in hospital the next
OL,10,Fday.
OL,12,FAn excerpt of Stockton's 999 call,
OL,13,Freleased by the Crown Prosecution
OL,14,FService (CPS), was played to the jury
OL,16,FRoberts pleaded guilty to neglect
OL,17,Fduring the trial.
