OL,6,FShe admitted failing to seek medical
OL,7,Fhelp for her little boy in December
OL,8,F2023 and January this year after he
OL,9,Fsuffered injuries to his private parts
OL,10,Fand to his ear.
OL,12,FJurors were told that Charlie suffered
OL,13,Fbruising in the months before his
OL,14,Fdeath.
OL,16,FIn August, five months prior to his
OL,17,Fmurder, Roberts expressed concerns to
OL,18,Fher brother about Stockton and said
OL,19,Fshe had installed the spy camera,
OL,20,Fhidden in a pot plant.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/15
