OL,6,FThe CPS has released this footage from
OL,7,FChristopher Stockton's police
OL,8,Finterview, which has been shown to the
OL,9,Fjury
OL,11,FDr Deborah Stalker, an expert
OL,12,Fpaediatrician and specialist in child
OL,13,Fprotection, studied photos of Charlie
OL,14,Fwhile was alive, medical experts and
OL,15,Fpost-mortem images.
OL,17,FShe told the jury she did not believe
OL,18,Fthat Charlie suffered a bruised ear
OL,19,Fwhile sleep-walking.
