OL,4,Cof partner's toddler son
OL,6,FShe said: "In my opinion, this is a
OL,7,Fnon-accidental injury, by that I mean
OL,8,Fit is a purposefully-inflicted injury.
OL,10,F"Accidental injuries to the ear are
OL,11,Fvery rare."
OL,13,FMr Justice Goss will sentence the pair
OL,14,Fnext month, once reports have been
OL,15,Fprepared on Roberts.
OL,17,FStockton was told that a life sentence
OL,18,Fwas inevitable, with the judge needing
OL,19,Fto set a minimum term.
