OL,6,FThe judge thanked the jury for their
OL,7,F"care" in dealing with this "upsetting
OL,8,Fcase".
OL,10,FOutside court, Charlie's dad Barry
OL,11,FGreenwell said: "Charlie was a much-
OL,12,Floved son and grandson who has been
OL,13,Ftaken away needlessly and has left the
OL,14,Fwhole family with a void that will
OL,15,Fnever be filled.
OL,17,F"As a family we are processing the
OL,18,Frecent events and are trying to come
OL,19,Fto terms with the verdict and
OL,20,Finformation given that has been deeply
OL,21,Fdisturbing to ourselves."
