OL,6,FDominic Tate, of CPS North East, said:
OL,7,F"It is clear from the evidence in this
OL,8,Fcase that Christopher Stockton
OL,9,Fmurdered Charlie Roberts.
OL,11,F"After being left in charge of Charlie
OL,12,Fat 8.45am, our case was that he lost
OL,13,Fhis temper within that crucial twenty
OL,14,Fminutes preceding his emergency call,
OL,15,Fbefore throwing Charlie with
OL,16,Fsufficient violence to cause
OL,17,Fcatastrophic head injuries."
